'''Gunter Faure''' is a leading [[geochemistry|geochemist]] who currently holds the position of Professor Emeritus in the School of Earth Science of [[Ohio State University]]. He obtained his PhD from the [[Massachusetts Institute of Technology]] in 1961.<ref>[http://www.earthsciences.osu.edu/faculty_bios.php?id=15 Gunter Faure at OSU]</ref>

